name: ME+YOU Series: "It's a Small World." Greeting Card
description:
4.5'x6.8' Folded greeting cards with A7 black envelopes
Hand-drawn with sumi-ink, Front & back
Blank interior
Plastic sealed sleeve packaging

The two lines represent two strangers and show how their fate intertwine in their lifetime.  Two paths cross once, coming from totally different places - meaning "It's a Small World."

Each artworks are original, hand-drawn and signed by the artist. Every card is unique and different.
